name: Daydreaming Under The Night Sky
description:
Elemental of the world part #3 : Air/Wind


sometimes i just want to lay down on the grass, gazing to the night sky, and forget about everything, 
forget about the future, forget about the past, just be here, be present.

watching the clouds moving slowly, counting the stars, and surrender to the void.
feel the wind blows, that all you need to do.
Contemplate, breathe, relax and surrender.
or maybe have some cigar to ease your mind. just lay down, and surrender.
